body:
Fixing reco sequence after changes made in https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/24380.
To speed-up reconstruction, instead of having pfNoPileUpJMETask back I've made an empty pf collection using a GenericPFCandidateSelector. To speed-up even more I made an inputEtMin cut on all the unneeded jet algorithms (ak4PF, ak4PFCHS, ak8PFCHS).
@cfmcginn @mandrenguyen
